{"tid":2362464,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"山頂羅馬水庫10年前被拆 水署瞞古蹟價值","createTime":"2021-01-11T12:45:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T06:09:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"109b6aea21c79c330c65c7194f845540a5956a1d","tid":2362464,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T12:45:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210107/6WZ4GXZQUNDOBKJR63WAPU5VB4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210107%2F6WZ4GXZQUNDOBKJR63WAPU5VB4%2F&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BQX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=8d2412b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210107%2F6WZ4GXZQUNDOBKJR63WAPU5VB4%2F&h=70f38698\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210107/6WZ4GXZQUNDOBKJR63WAPU5VB4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n山頂羅馬水庫10年前被拆 水署瞞古蹟價值<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/UpuPJOVJUGzoaDjoNUO9_BQlON0=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7UZQUSBJ4NGP7L647CA5EYKFAQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FUpuPJOVJUGzoaDjoNUO9_BQlON0%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7UZQUSBJ4NGP7L647CA5EYKFAQ.jpg&h=338bc852&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■水務署06/07年報曾刊登山頂克頓道食水配水庫照片，又指已完成配水庫的磚內襯全面影像檔案，顯示水務署清楚其價值。水務署年報圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】深水埗主教山配水庫百年古蹟因公眾叫停而逃過變廢墟的命運，但山頂另一座同樣逾百年的古羅馬式配水庫，原來早在10年前已被水務署完全拆毀，而古蹟辦當年被諮詢時亦同意清拆，只保留兩條支柱及拱頂的紅磚。但立法會文件顯示，水務署曾隱瞞配水庫的古蹟價值。<br />\n<br />\n水務署2006/07年報在「保護文物」段落曾刊登山頂克頓道食水配水庫照片，照片中的水庫同樣以古羅馬式建築風格建造，年報又表示已完成配水庫的磚內襯全面影像檔案，顯示水務署清楚配水庫的文物價值。<br />\n<br />\n水務署昨回覆查詢時卻表示，該座建1908年的山頂克頓道食水配水庫，面積約540平方米，以紅磚鋪蓋圍牆內壁和建造支柱及拱。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「古諮會同公眾完全唔知件事」<br />\n<br />\n水務署指因應近日社會對深水埗減壓缸的關注，發展局常任秘書長將領導一個工作小組，檢視部門在處理事件上的情況及提出改善，避免同類事件再發生。<br />\n<br />\n立法會文件顯示，水務署2007年4月曾向財委會申請撥款約2億元，進行港島半。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n港大建築學院文物保護課程學部主任李浩然形容事件「好大鑊，咁就拆左個古蹟」，認為事件反映部門的溝通出現嚴重問題， 「古蹟辦冇提交文件予古諮會討論，古諮會同公眾人士完全唔知件事」，認為必須盡快檢討現行機制是否有漏洞。"},{"pid":"30d95530c71a29d9e3a365e910004398be7e4f4b","tid":2362464,"uid":17008,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T13:26:17.000Z","msg":"肯定有人會知有價值 但開聲講完 上頭暗示唔想寫report有排跟 搞咁多野"},{"pid":"7f0e83ea4a22dd9d0413d3a3556a910a4d9bddb7","tid":2362464,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T13:41:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a789bb9d3d322689b89ee0cde26e0b9dac9a47d","tid":2362464,"uid":301707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T04:28:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d807c91c3a2986469424efe8e9ea86ec03e16e75","tid":2362464,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T04:31:56.000Z","msg":"只保留兩條柱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e3e612b353da63b918a104ab6719e4edae3b03b","tid":2362464,"uid":271397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T04:34:45.000Z","msg":"呢個水庫個vault 好似仲完整啲"},{"pid":"7b487780c2e7d9e070d03c63bd0f95a4ca5b1995","tid":2362464,"uid":16981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T06:05:16.000Z","msg":"屌佢哋老母真係仆街嚟架喎<br />\n知唔知啲古蹟幾珍貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f951f820d455508c987f803da0b50cc5409d147","tid":2362464,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2